(14, NULL, NULL, 'Abies', NULL, NULL, 'magnifica', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Asian abies do poorly in Portland (at the Hoyt) due to too little summer rain. Also do poorly at UBC as the soil is not deep enough and they need to be able to put their roots down deep to live more than 20 years. On the other hand, European Abies do very well here. ', '', NULL, NULL, 'discussed & eliminated', '', 'trees - conifers', '', '', '', 'Eliminated', 'no', 'not garden adaptable in our region', '', '', '', 'No', ''),
