ers or Solidago. It is also quite useful as an edging for borders. It''s medium-sized, round leaves contrast well with the fine foliage and textures of ornamental grasses or woody shrubs like, Nandina, hebes and barberry.', '', NULL, NULL, 'Justice, Jones, Hammond', '2003', 'Perennials - Bulbs', '', '', 'Plant Finder 2006-2007', 'GPP', '', 'border sm. collect. - 8/06 moved to 2008', '2009', '', '', 'Yes', '');
