(1421, NULL, NULL, 'Schizophragma', NULL, NULL, 'hydrangeoides', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Moonlight', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '', NULL, '', '', 'vine', 'deciduous', '', '', '', '', '', 'summer', '', '', '', '', '', '35', '', '', '5', '8', '', 'Full sun to 3/4 day shade.', 'Silver moonlight patterns on the leaves make this self-clinging and well-behaved vine stand out. White lace-cap hydrangea flowers in mid-summer create a graceful and elegant look. Excellent to grow up trees or on mason walls or fences. Disease and pest resistant.', '', NULL, NULL, 'Vergara', '2001', 'Shrubs - Vines', '', '', '', 'GPP', '', '', '2001', '', '', 'Yes', ''),
